      },
      "date": "2024-02-26 19:58:29.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(3 comments)\n\nTim, thanks for working on this.  It is definitely an improvement over the first version of the patch, and allows at least side-by-side comparison of the different versions of the patches to the checkpatch script.\n\nI was originally thinking that this patch would introduce only a single \"contrib/scripts/checkpatch-lustre.patch\" file that was generated from the current script changes (what you currently have in \"patch-v4.12-11743-g96d0d83\"), and that file would be updated to reflect the changes applied to the new checkpatch.pl script when it is updated (i.e. change \"checkpatch-lustre.patch\" to what is now \"patch-v6.8-rc5-gb401b62175\" as part of the next patch).\n\nThat would simplify the comparison of changes to the Lustre-specific patch from one version to the next, independent of the changes to the checkpatch.pl script itself.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
